oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Avicultural Management - Part II Consultation for the Distant Aviculturist
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Clipsham, Robert C.
Thompson, Dale R.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: It seems as though, in our push to investigate and share new concepts and discoveries on every front of aviculture, we tend to overlook what projects may be currently underway. Such is the case with the avicultural consultation program which we initiated over a year ago with great expectations. We would like to share the results of this non-traditional concept to demonstrate to other interested aviculturists what one pioneer has to show...
